data.description: Spacious Clayton Home Manufactured Home nestled in the trees. Home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Very open concept with the kitchen open to the den and living room. Kitchen has tons of cabinet and counter top space and a great island for entertaining. Laundry room off the kitchen has plenty of storage space! Split floor plan has the master bedroom on one side and 3 bedrooms on the other side of the home. Master Bedroom boasts a very spacious en suite bathroom and walk in closet. Front yard has been fenced and sodded. Home has a small covered front porch. There is a full ramp the runs from the driveway along the side of the house to the amazing covered back deck.
